originalText.text: The recruiters I worked with were always quick to respond and thoughtful of their recommendations. When I needed to end an assignment early (ill matched) they made the arrangements quickly and without issue. I would recommend this agency.

originalText.text: TalentHub is worth going to. They have very good jobs available (depending on what you are looking for)..The recruiters I worked with were quick to responding e-mails. They always kept me updated on the status of my candidacy and are very professional. It took a while to find the perfect match but they really came through. Thank you TalentHub.

originalText.text: The people are friendly, but  you  expect women recruiters to be silver-tongued nice sales people. They do return calls and e-mails better than other  staffing agencies. However they are behind the ball, late to the game with their clients. The two positions they wanted to submit me  for ,  one alredy had candidates interviewing for 2nd rounds and the second position was filled before even they had a chance to submit my resume or it.  This is a lower-end staffing agency for low-level clerical office workers. They want you to come in to interview with them to screen you, so dress professionally.
